<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Audit Logs - 777 Heaven Records</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
            color: #e4e4e7;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .header {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .breadcrumb {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            align-items: center;
            color: #a1a1aa;
        }

        .breadcrumb a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .btn-sm {
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: #e4e4e7;
        }

        .btn-danger {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.8);
            color: white;
        }

        .toolbar {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .toolbar h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .logs-container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .log-entry {
            padding: 1rem;
            border-left: 3px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.5);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .log-entry:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border-left-color: #667eea;
        }

        .log-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .log-action {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .log-timestamp {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #a1a1aa;
        }

        .log-details {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #d4d4d8;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        .log-meta {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #a1a1aa;
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .badge {
            padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .badge-create { background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2); color: #22c55e; }
        .badge-archive { background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.2); color: #fbbf24; }
        .badge-unarchive { background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); color: #3b82f6; }
        .badge-soft_delete { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2); color: #ef4444; }
        .badge-restore { background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2); color: #22c55e; }
        .badge-permanent_delete { background: rgba(127, 29, 29, 0.5); color: #fca5a5; }
        .badge-status_update { background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.2); color: #a855f7; }

        .empty-state {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            color: #a1a1aa;
        }

        .empty-state h3 {
            color: #e4e4e7;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .toolbar {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1rem;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            .log-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 0.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üéµ 777 Heaven Records</h1>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
            <a href="/admin/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">Dashboard</a>
            <a href="/admin/logout" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm">Logout</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="breadcrumb">
            <a href="/admin/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
            <span>/</span>
            <span>Audit Logs</span>
        </div>

        <a href="/admin/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">‚Üê Back to Dashboard</a>

        <div class="toolbar">
            <h2>üìã Activity Audit Logs</h2>
            <div style="color: #a1a1aa; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                Showing last <%= logs.length %> activities
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="logs-container">
            <% if (logs.length === 0) { %>
                <div class="empty-state">
                    <h3>No Activity Logs</h3>
                    <p>No activity has been recorded yet.</p>
                </div>
            <% } else { %>
                <% logs.forEach(log => { %>
                    <div class="log-entry">
                        <div class="log-header">
                            <div>
                                <span class="badge badge-<%= log.action %>">
                                    <%= log.action.replace('_', ' ').toUpperCase() %>
                                </span>
                                <span class="log-action" style="margin-left: 0.5rem;">
                                    <%= log.details %>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="log-timestamp">
                                <%= new Date(log.timestamp).toLocaleString() %>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="log-meta">
                            <span>üë§ Admin: <strong><%= log.adminUsername %></strong></span>
                            <% if (log.submissionId) { %>
                                <span>üìÑ Submission: <strong><%= log.submissionId %></strong></span>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2); border-radius: 12px;">
            <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">üìä About Audit Logs</h3>
            <p style="color: #a1a1aa; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                Audit logs track all significant actions performed by administrators in the system. 
                This includes creating, archiving, deleting, restoring submissions, and status updates. 
                The system automatically maintains a record of who performed each action and when it occurred, 
                providing accountability and transparency.
            </p>
            <p style="color: #a1a1aa; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 0.75rem;">
                The system retains the last 1,000 log entries to prevent excessive file growth.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
